        <abstract>
            <p>CD is allowing his family to decide whether Chauncey Wright’s paper on Mivart is dull.</p>
            <p>Health and despondency.</p> 
<p>Doubts his ability to answer Mivart successfully [in 6th ed. of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>].</p> 
